## Hot vs. Cold Changes

| Change | Type | Effect |
|--------|------|--------|
| `control_system.writes_enabled` | Hot | Hooks re-read on each call |
| `control_system.limits_checking.enabled` | Hot | Hooks re-read on each call |
| `control_system.limits_checking.allow_unlisted_channels` | Hot | Hooks re-read on each call |
| `approval.mode` | Hot | Hooks re-read on each call |
| `control_system.type` | Cold | Requires MCP server restart |
| `archiver.*` | Cold | Requires MCP server restart |
| `.mcp.json` changes | Cold | Requires new Claude Code session |
| `.claude/settings.json` | Cold | Requires new Claude Code session |
| Hook scripts | Cold | Requires new Claude Code session |

