## Escalation Rules

**Do NOT attempt to fix** (escalate to operator):
- Permission/authentication issues with external services
- Network connectivity problems
- Missing Python dependencies
- Corrupted config files (invalid YAML/JSON)
- Issues requiring changes to `.claude/settings.json` or hook scripts (use `osprey claude regen`)

**Always confirm before**:
- Changing `control_system.writes_enabled` (safety-critical)
- Modifying `.mcp.json` server entries (requires session restart)
- Any change that could affect production control system access
